        "From toddlers just learning to call 'Papa,' to bigger children who could go out to hail rickshaws, to old folks with white whiskers — who wouldn't immediately taste something sweet and rich at the mention of Laba porridge? Mix millet, beans, dates, chestnuts, sugar, and peanuts together, boil them into a bubbling pot that seems to sigh as it simmers — just watching and smelling it is enough to make you swallow three times!",
